---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Use | Proxilyt"
  description="Terms of Use for Proxilyt Local SEO Analytics"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-slate-100">
    <Header isHome={false} />

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="flex-1 max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full px-6 py-16 sm:px-8 sm:py-20">
      <h1
        class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4"
        style="font-family: 'League Spartan', sans-serif;"
      >
        Terms of Use
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-12">
        Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none text-gray-700">
        <p>
          Welcome to Proxilyt (“Company”, “we”, “our”, “us”).
          <br /> These Terms of Service (“Terms”) govern your access to and use of
          the Proxilyt website, dashboard, tools, and services (collectively, the
          “Service”). By creating an account or using the Service, you agree to be
          bound by these Terms. If you do not agree, you may not use the Service.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Eligibility</h2>
        <p>
          You must be at least 18 years old to use the Service.
          <br />
          By using Proxilyt, you represent and warrant that:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>You are at least 18 years old.</li>
          <li>
            You have the legal capacity to enter into a binding agreement.
          </li>
          <li>You are using the Service for lawful business purposes.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          Description of Services
        </h2>
        <p>Proxilyt provides:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Local SEO ranking analysis</li>
          <li>Competitive analysis tools</li>
          <li>Business listing tracking</li>
          <li>Related digital marketing analytics tools</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">Future features may include:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Google Business Profile management</li>
          <li>Google Ads handling</li>
          <li>Additional SEO and marketing services</li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue features at
          any time.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          Account Registration
        </h2>
        <p>To use the Service, you must create an account.</p>
        <br />
        <p>You agree to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Provide accurate and complete information</li>
          <li>Keep login credentials confidential</li>
          <li>Be responsible for all activity under your account</li>
        </ul>
        <br />
        <p>
          We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that provide
          false information or violate these Terms.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          Fees & Payments
        </h2>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">
          1. Freemium Model
        </h3>
        <p>
          Proxilyt currently operates under a freemium model. Certain features
          or higher query limits may require payment.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">
          2. Manual Payments
        </h3>
        <p>At present:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Payments may be accepted manually via UPI.</li>
          <li>
            Upon receipt of payment, query limits may be manually adjusted.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">
          3. Future Payment Integration
        </h3>
        <p>
          We may integrate third-party payment processors (such as Stripe) in
          the future. By continuing to use paid features, you agree to comply
          with their terms as applicable.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          Refund Policy
        </h2>
        <p>
          Refunds may be issued at our discretion. If you believe you were
          incorrectly charged or unsatisfied with a paid feature, you may
          contact: <a
            href="mailto:main.proxilyt@gmail.com"
            class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">main.proxilyt@gmail.com</a
          >
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          We reserve the right to deny refund requests in cases of abuse or
          misuse of the Service.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          Acceptable Use
        </h2>
        <p>You agree NOT to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Use the Service for unlawful purposes</li>
          <li>Attempt to reverse engineer or scrape the platform</li>
          <li>Interfere with system security</li>
          <li>Use automated bots to overload the system</li>
          <li>Misrepresent business information</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Violation may result in account termination without notice.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
          Data Accuracy Disclaimer
        </h2>
        <p>
          SEO rankings and analytics are estimates based on available data. We
          do not guarantee:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Ranking improvements</li>
          <li>Traffic increases</li>
          <li>Revenue growth</li>
          <li>Accuracy of third-party data sources</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">
          You acknowledge that search engine rankings fluctuate and are outside
          our control.
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Intellectual Property
          </h2>
          <p>
            All content, branding, software, design, and algorithms are the
            property of Proxilyt. You may not:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Copy</li>
            <li>Modify</li>
            <li>Distribute</li>
            <li>Resell</li>
            <li>Reverse engineer</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">Any unauthorized use may result in legal action.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Limitation of Liability
          </h2>
          <p>To the maximum extent permitted under Indian law:</p>
          <br />
          <p>Proxilyt shall not be liable for:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Loss of profits</li>
            <li>Loss of business opportunities</li>
            <li>Data loss</li>
            <li>Indirect or consequential damages</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Our total liability shall not exceed the amount paid by you in the
            preceding 3 months.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Indemnification
          </h2>
          <p>
            You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Proxilyt from any claims
            arising from:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Your misuse of the Service</li>
            <li>Violation of these Terms</li>
            <li>Violation of applicable laws</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Termination
          </h2>
          <p>We may suspend or terminate your account at any time if:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>You violate these Terms</li>
            <li>You misuse the Service</li>
            <li>We discontinue operations</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">You may terminate your account by emailing us.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Arbitration & Governing Law
          </h2>
          <p>These Terms shall be governed by the laws of India.</p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Any disputes shall be resolved through binding arbitration in
            Panchkula, Haryana, India. You waive the right to participate in
            class-action lawsuits.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Modification of Terms of Use
          </h2>
          <p>
            We can amend these Terms of Use at any time and will update these
            Terms of Use in the event of any such amendments. It is your sole
            responsibility to check the Site from time to time to view any such
            changes in this agreement. Your continued use of the Site or the
            Service signifies your agreement to our revisions to these Terms of
            Use. We will endeavor to notify you of material changes to the Terms
            by posting a notice on our homepage and/or sending an email to the
            email address you provided to us upon registration. For this
            additional reason, you should keep your contact and profile
            information current. Any changes to these Terms (other than as set
            forth in this paragraph) or waiver of our rights hereunder shall not
            be valid or effective except in a written agreement bearing the
            physical signature of one of our officers. No purported waiver or
            modification of this agreement on our part via telephonic or email
            communications shall be valid.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Contact Information
          </h2>
          <p>
            Proxilyt<br />
            Panchkula, Haryana, India<br />
            <a
              href="mailto:main.proxilyt@gmail.com"
              class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">main.proxilyt@gmail.com</a
            >
          </p>
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
    <!-- Footer -->
    <Footer />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
